dcterms:description: A densely annotated dataset for Event Temporal Relation Classification, focusing on event temporal relations across sentences. It includes six temporal relations: AFTER, BEFORE, INCLUDE, IS INCLUDED, VAGUE, and SIMULTANEOUS.
